1
00:01:33,400 --> 00:01:34,880
[OVERDO]

2
00:01:35,340 --> 00:01:37,830
[Episode 10]

3
00:02:04,850 --> 00:02:06,720
♪ I happened to ♪

4
00:02:06,740 --> 00:02:08,600
♪ Hear your name ♪

5
00:02:09,960 --> 00:02:11,690
♪ And all the memories ♪

6
00:02:11,740 --> 00:02:14,960
♪ Came flooding back ♪

7
00:02:15,530 --> 00:02:17,350
♪ There I stood in the falling snow ♪

8
00:02:17,430 --> 00:02:20,010
♪ Wrapped in my coat ♪

9
00:02:20,500 --> 00:02:22,700
♪ My heart pounding ♪

10
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:25,190
Young Master Qingyi,
you really have excellent taste.

11
00:02:25,020 --> 00:02:26,810
♪ Walking down that old road ♪

12
00:02:25,910 --> 00:02:27,310
Miss Fang looks absolutely stunning

13
00:02:26,829 --> 00:02:28,590
♪ Stopping every few steps ♪

14
00:02:27,520 --> 00:02:28,750
in this gown.

15
00:02:30,050 --> 00:02:31,900
♪ In the misty train car ♪

16
00:02:31,920 --> 00:02:35,480
♪ I wish I could ask you once more ♪

17
00:02:36,370 --> 00:02:40,260
♪ If you have any ♪

18
00:02:40,370 --> 00:02:42,870
♪ New corny jokes to tell ♪

19
00:02:48,310 --> 00:02:49,910
So this is where you were shot

20
00:02:50,870 --> 00:02:51,960
3 years ago.

21
00:02:56,030 --> 00:02:56,800
Looks like

22
00:02:57,310 --> 00:02:59,310
you're not only ruthless to others—

23
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:01,560
you're even more ruthless to yourself.

24
00:03:03,630 --> 00:03:04,630
Had your fill yet?

25
00:03:18,710 --> 00:03:20,030
This suit and wedding gown

26
00:03:20,030 --> 00:03:21,160
are a perfect match.

27
00:03:22,960 --> 00:03:23,840
What a pity.

28
00:03:25,870 --> 00:03:27,150
If there's anything
you're unsatisfied with,

29
00:03:27,150 --> 00:03:28,480
I can make adjustments.

30
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:30,420
It's a pity that my brother

31
00:03:30,430 --> 00:03:31,890
went to see another woman.

32
00:03:37,470 --> 00:03:38,910
The gown doesn't quite fit.

33
00:03:38,910 --> 00:03:39,840
It's a bit loose.

34
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:42,470
This is an off-the-rack gown.

35
00:03:42,470 --> 00:03:43,800
We can take Miss Fang's measurements

36
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:44,840
and tailor it.

37
00:03:45,120 --> 00:03:46,380
I'll do the measuring.

38
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:49,890
Measuring tape.

39
00:04:04,560 --> 00:04:06,160
Thirty-eight centimeters.

40
00:04:11,910 --> 00:04:13,110
You're really crazy.

41
00:04:13,520 --> 00:04:14,780
They're all watching.

42
00:04:20,630 --> 00:04:21,560
Miss Fang,

43
00:04:22,310 --> 00:04:24,240
why have you lost weight recently?

44
00:04:25,560 --> 00:04:27,430
Are you really going to put on...

45
00:04:29,190 --> 00:04:31,850
such a vulgar display
in front of so many people?

46
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:38,830
You're right.

47
00:04:41,040 --> 00:04:42,870
Someone as beautiful as Miss Fang

48
00:04:42,870 --> 00:04:45,000
shouldn't be on display for everyone.

49
00:04:46,159 --> 00:04:46,680
Get out.

50
00:04:48,310 --> 00:04:48,870
Yes.

51
00:04:49,040 --> 00:04:49,570
Let's go.

52
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:59,200
Whether you accept it or not,

53
00:04:59,950 --> 00:05:01,480
I'm marrying your brother.

54
00:05:02,270 --> 00:05:04,530
Don't do something this childish again.

55
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:06,060
A man who leaves you behind

56
00:05:06,390 --> 00:05:08,560
to fuss over another woman—

57
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:11,220
are you sure you want to marry him?

58
00:05:12,950 --> 00:05:14,430
You mean Ms. Ye, right?

59
00:05:17,950 --> 00:05:18,800
Students,

60
00:05:19,190 --> 00:05:21,310
throughout history, humanity

61
00:05:21,560 --> 00:05:24,190
has long dreamed of flying into the sky.

62
00:05:24,430 --> 00:05:25,720
And today, that dream

63
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:27,750
is no longer just

64
00:05:27,870 --> 00:05:30,200
a romantic desire to explore the unknown.

65
00:05:30,360 --> 00:05:31,510
It has become

66
00:05:31,720 --> 00:05:33,120
a noble mission to defend

67
00:05:33,270 --> 00:05:34,480
our nation through aviation.

68
00:05:34,480 --> 00:05:35,070
Right?

69
00:05:35,070 --> 00:05:36,480
Right!

70
00:05:40,310 --> 00:05:41,430
Does anyone know

71
00:05:41,630 --> 00:05:43,159
how to make a paper airplane

72
00:05:43,159 --> 00:05:44,430
fly high and far?

73
00:05:44,430 --> 00:05:45,560
No.

74
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:47,870
It depends on how you fold it.

75
00:05:48,190 --> 00:05:49,390
Ms. Ye is right.

76
00:05:49,920 --> 00:05:52,000
If you want your paper airplane
to fly high and far,

77
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:52,600
the way you fold it

78
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:54,360
makes a huge difference.

79
00:05:57,190 --> 00:05:59,360
This is a glider-type plane.

80
00:05:59,600 --> 00:06:01,750
It can stay aloft at high altitude
for a long time.

81
00:06:01,750 --> 00:06:02,310
However,

82
00:06:02,600 --> 00:06:04,200
if it runs into strong winds,

83
00:06:04,240 --> 00:06:05,500
it won't fly very well.

84
00:06:11,120 --> 00:06:11,560
Look.

85
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:13,390
Here's another design.

86
00:06:13,630 --> 00:06:15,360
We just need to make
one change to the wing.

87
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:16,360
And what is it?

88
00:06:16,360 --> 00:06:18,430
-The shape of the wings.
-The shape.

89
00:06:18,630 --> 00:06:19,800
Change the shape of the wings

90
00:06:19,800 --> 00:06:20,830
to reduce drag.

91
00:06:22,160 --> 00:06:23,870
With this high-speed design,

92
00:06:23,870 --> 00:06:26,130
you can also adjust the nose of the plane.

93
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:27,560
But while pursuing speed,

94
00:06:27,560 --> 00:06:29,870
you'll inevitably sacrifice
some stability.

95
00:06:29,870 --> 00:06:30,830
This design

96
00:06:30,830 --> 00:06:33,040
is best suited for someone
as skilled as our principal.

97
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:35,240
Because it takes real technique to fold

98
00:06:35,440 --> 00:06:36,390
and

99
00:06:36,820 --> 00:06:38,190
real skill to throw.

100
00:06:38,830 --> 00:06:40,260
In a moment, write your wishes

101
00:06:40,260 --> 00:06:41,590
on the paper airplanes,

102
00:06:42,159 --> 00:06:43,680
and then we'll launch them together,

103
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:44,600
okay?

104
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,800
Okay!

105
00:06:49,190 --> 00:06:49,850
Principal,

106
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:51,540
what did you write?

107
00:06:54,240 --> 00:06:55,210
I wrote,

108
00:06:56,830 --> 00:06:58,560
"I hope Ms. Ye's paper airplane

109
00:06:59,430 --> 00:07:00,820
flies the highest."

110
00:07:46,510 --> 00:07:48,680
I noticed it
when the aviation school opened.

111
00:07:48,680 --> 00:07:51,080
Your brother treats her very differently.

112
00:07:51,750 --> 00:07:52,720
So what?

113
00:07:55,600 --> 00:07:58,510
A marriage alliance has always been about
binding interests together—

114
00:07:58,510 --> 00:08:00,570
no one cares about genuine feelings,

115
00:08:00,630 --> 00:08:03,360
especially not
in a prominent family like yours.

116
00:08:03,990 --> 00:08:07,250
Besides, it's livelier
with another sister in the family.

117
00:08:09,720 --> 00:08:11,580
You're so tolerant of my brother,

118
00:08:11,830 --> 00:08:13,960
yet you won't allow me anything at all?

119
00:08:15,390 --> 00:08:16,510
That's how marriage alliances

120
00:08:16,510 --> 00:08:17,560
work.

121
00:08:17,830 --> 00:08:20,230
Young Master Qingyi, surely you know that.

122
00:08:28,120 --> 00:08:29,980
Only those with ulterior motives

123
00:08:30,270 --> 00:08:32,799
can endure
what ordinary people never would.

124
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:39,150
Could it be

125
00:08:39,880 --> 00:08:41,600
that you want to use my brother
the same way

126
00:08:41,600 --> 00:08:42,600
you used me 3 years ago?

127
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:43,669
You're hurting me.

128
00:08:44,440 --> 00:08:45,480
I'm warning you—

129
00:08:46,270 --> 00:08:47,200
if you dare,

130
00:08:47,390 --> 00:08:48,600
I will kill you.

131
00:08:53,840 --> 00:08:56,240
You're snapping at your brother every day,

132
00:08:56,360 --> 00:08:59,020
but deep down,
you actually care about him a lot.

133
00:08:59,270 --> 00:09:00,320
What I care about

134
00:09:01,270 --> 00:09:03,030
is making sure you don't treat my brother

135
00:09:03,030 --> 00:09:04,290
the way you treated me.

136
00:09:05,670 --> 00:09:06,600
Treat him how?

137
00:09:10,200 --> 00:09:11,080
Like this?

138
00:09:18,720 --> 00:09:20,050
Are you done measuring?

139
00:09:27,630 --> 00:09:29,080
I remember all your measurements.

140
00:09:29,080 --> 00:09:30,000
No need to measure again.

141
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:31,320
But I still don't know

142
00:09:31,440 --> 00:09:32,510
your brother's measurements.

143
00:09:32,510 --> 00:09:33,390
Ren Susu.

144
00:09:35,200 --> 00:09:36,030
I mean,

145
00:09:36,670 --> 00:09:37,750
this suit.

146
00:09:38,480 --> 00:09:40,410
I wonder if it'll fit your brother.

147
00:09:41,670 --> 00:09:43,270
You don't quite fill it out.

148
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:46,010
I'm warning you—

149
00:09:47,510 --> 00:09:48,970
stay away from my brother.

150
00:10:08,390 --> 00:10:09,050
Principal,

151
00:10:10,480 --> 00:10:11,550
have you set a date

152
00:10:12,030 --> 00:10:13,030
for your wedding?

153
00:10:17,840 --> 00:10:18,390
Yes.

154
00:10:24,320 --> 00:10:25,380
Congratulations.

155
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:31,440
I remember

156
00:10:31,790 --> 00:10:34,450
we talked about
our New Year's wishes last year.

157
00:10:35,720 --> 00:10:37,440
Now the aviation school
has gained public recognition

158
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:38,840
and valuable resources.

159
00:10:39,480 --> 00:10:39,960
And I

160
00:10:40,360 --> 00:10:42,620
have trained my first batch of students.

161
00:10:44,240 --> 00:10:46,840
We've both made
each other's wishes come true.

162
00:10:53,910 --> 00:10:54,720
You're right.

163
00:10:58,600 --> 00:10:59,390
Thank you

164
00:11:00,440 --> 00:11:02,770
for coming to support my volunteer class.

165
00:11:10,600 --> 00:11:12,400
No need to see me off any further.

166
00:12:11,120 --> 00:12:11,910
We...

167
00:12:13,630 --> 00:12:15,890
are not on the same flight path after all.

168
00:13:09,890 --> 00:13:10,480
Mother,

169
00:13:11,000 --> 00:13:11,530
I'm here.

170
00:13:15,150 --> 00:13:16,070
Come on, come here.

171
00:13:16,070 --> 00:13:17,000
Why'd you come?

172
00:13:17,080 --> 00:13:17,510
Sit.

173
00:13:18,120 --> 00:13:19,200
Jinrui, you've been doing skincare
day and night.

174
00:13:19,200 --> 00:13:21,600
Are you determined to
look younger than me?

175
00:13:22,240 --> 00:13:23,500
You don't understand.

176
00:13:23,600 --> 00:13:24,790
Back when I

177
00:13:24,960 --> 00:13:27,020
lived in the countryside, my skin was

178
00:13:27,200 --> 00:13:28,510
constantly exposed to the sun and wind.

179
00:13:28,510 --> 00:13:29,870
It felt like sandpaper.

180
00:13:30,080 --> 00:13:31,680
I have to take care of my skin.

181
00:13:32,470 --> 00:13:33,150
Boze,

182
00:13:33,790 --> 00:13:34,750
you came so early.

183
00:13:34,750 --> 00:13:35,810
What's the matter?

184
00:13:37,240 --> 00:13:38,600
My father from the Li family has returned.

185
00:13:38,600 --> 00:13:39,400
He's inviting

186
00:13:39,550 --> 00:13:40,550
everyone over.

187
00:13:44,550 --> 00:13:45,480
I'm observing a vegetarian fast,

188
00:13:45,480 --> 00:13:46,750
so I'll pass.

189
00:13:49,840 --> 00:13:51,030
If Mother doesn't want to go,

190
00:13:51,030 --> 00:13:51,840
that's fine.

191
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:53,800
Let Qingyu and Qingyi go with me.

192
00:13:56,790 --> 00:13:58,030
Qingyu has been

193
00:13:58,030 --> 00:13:59,510
busy with the aviation school lately.

194
00:13:59,510 --> 00:14:00,600
He has no time to go.

195
00:14:02,030 --> 00:14:03,240
As for Qingyi...

196
00:14:05,030 --> 00:14:05,830
in the future,

197
00:14:06,270 --> 00:14:08,870
you don't need to
bring him back to your family.

198
00:14:09,670 --> 00:14:10,390
Mother,

199
00:14:11,480 --> 00:14:12,150
Qingyi

200
00:14:13,120 --> 00:14:14,910
grew up in the Li family

201
00:14:15,240 --> 00:14:16,840
and has lived with Father Li
for over 10 years.

202
00:14:16,840 --> 00:14:18,150
They've surely formed a bond.

203
00:14:18,150 --> 00:14:18,870
He must

204
00:14:18,870 --> 00:14:20,470
miss Father Li very much too.

205
00:14:21,840 --> 00:14:23,040
Don't worry, Mother.

206
00:14:23,550 --> 00:14:25,080
I'll definitely take good care of Qingyi.

207
00:14:25,080 --> 00:14:26,010
We're brothers.

208
00:14:26,720 --> 00:14:28,390
Even though he doesn't see me
as his brother,

209
00:14:28,390 --> 00:14:29,600
I have to

210
00:14:29,600 --> 00:14:31,460
fulfill my duties as his brother.

211
00:14:40,120 --> 00:14:40,600
Qingyi.

212
00:14:41,630 --> 00:14:42,630
Father Li is back.

213
00:14:43,630 --> 00:14:44,910
He's missed you terribly.

214
00:14:44,910 --> 00:14:45,790
Come back with me

215
00:14:45,790 --> 00:14:46,790
to see him.

216
00:15:02,630 --> 00:15:03,430
Inspector Li.

217
00:15:06,910 --> 00:15:08,110
What brings you here?

218
00:15:08,150 --> 00:15:09,600
My father from the Li family has returned.

219
00:15:09,600 --> 00:15:10,440
I've come to invite Qingyi home

220
00:15:10,440 --> 00:15:11,770
for a family gathering.

221
00:15:13,120 --> 00:15:15,080
I heard Marshal Li is leading troops
in the field all year round.

222
00:15:15,080 --> 00:15:16,720
It's rare for him to return to Nancheng.

223
00:15:16,720 --> 00:15:18,790
You three should have a good reunion.

224
00:15:20,480 --> 00:15:21,630
But I didn't expect

225
00:15:22,600 --> 00:15:24,630
you to be this close to Marshal Li,

226
00:15:25,000 --> 00:15:26,320
even though you didn't

227
00:15:26,480 --> 00:15:27,810
grow up in the Li family.

228
00:15:29,320 --> 00:15:29,790
Yes.

229
00:15:30,360 --> 00:15:31,320
Although my father and I

230
00:15:31,320 --> 00:15:32,840
haven't spent much time together,

231
00:15:32,840 --> 00:15:35,150
we've always kept in touch
through letters and phone calls.

232
00:15:35,150 --> 00:15:36,270
He's always taught me

233
00:15:36,270 --> 00:15:37,960
to work hard in the police force

234
00:15:37,960 --> 00:15:39,550
and keep the area safe and well-governed

235
00:15:39,550 --> 00:15:41,610
so as not to disgrace his reputation.

236
00:15:42,120 --> 00:15:42,910
Naturally.

237
00:15:44,000 --> 00:15:45,730
So, is Marshal Li back this time

238
00:15:45,750 --> 00:15:47,750
for Young Master Qingyi's wedding?

239
00:15:50,270 --> 00:15:51,870
Marshal Li and the Huo family

240
00:15:52,240 --> 00:15:53,600
go way back, right?

241
00:15:53,910 --> 00:15:54,270
Yes.

242
00:15:55,000 --> 00:15:56,080
My father has long

243
00:15:56,080 --> 00:15:58,030
had dealings with the Huos
in the arms trade.

244
00:15:58,030 --> 00:15:58,960
My father is also one of
the founding members

245
00:15:58,960 --> 00:16:01,090
of the Huo family's Zunlan Elite Club.

246
00:16:04,320 --> 00:16:05,510
Elite Club?

247
00:16:08,720 --> 00:16:09,650
The Elite Club is

248
00:16:09,750 --> 00:16:11,600
an exclusive circle
the Huo family put together.

249
00:16:11,600 --> 00:16:12,750
The city's prominent families

250
00:16:12,750 --> 00:16:14,580
and influential merchants are all members.

251
00:16:14,580 --> 00:16:16,780
I've heard that the Huo family only does

252
00:16:17,120 --> 00:16:19,360
certain business with members of the club—

253
00:16:19,360 --> 00:16:21,290
outsiders have no standing there.

254
00:16:22,910 --> 00:16:24,000
I'm new to the city

255
00:16:24,240 --> 00:16:26,240
and would like to expand my network.

256
00:16:26,320 --> 00:16:27,790
Inspector Li, could you

257
00:16:28,080 --> 00:16:29,870
introduce me to the Elite Club?

258
00:16:33,000 --> 00:16:33,930
Unfortunately,

259
00:16:34,390 --> 00:16:35,630
I'm not a member.

260
00:16:36,360 --> 00:16:36,960
However,

261
00:16:37,960 --> 00:16:39,440
if you want to join,

262
00:16:40,080 --> 00:16:41,680
you could just ask my father.

263
00:16:43,550 --> 00:16:44,510
Then may I

264
00:16:44,670 --> 00:16:46,270
pay Marshal Li a visit today?

265
00:16:46,550 --> 00:16:47,080
Sure.

266
00:16:47,750 --> 00:16:48,750
I was just worried

267
00:16:48,840 --> 00:16:50,470
that with Mother and Qingyu both busy,

268
00:16:50,470 --> 00:16:51,790
it'd be far too dull with just Qingyi

269
00:16:51,790 --> 00:16:52,790
and me going home.

270
00:17:03,750 --> 00:17:04,270
Qingyi,

271
00:17:04,480 --> 00:17:05,280
are you ready?

272
00:17:06,589 --> 00:17:07,390
Get in the car.

273
00:17:09,550 --> 00:17:11,079
Miss Fang is coming with us.

274
00:17:12,680 --> 00:17:14,240
I've prepared some gifts for you.

275
00:17:14,240 --> 00:17:14,900
Take a look.

276
00:17:15,400 --> 00:17:17,329
I wonder if Uncle Li will like them.

277
00:17:22,240 --> 00:17:23,040
Don't bother.

278
00:17:23,829 --> 00:17:24,720
He won't like

279
00:17:24,790 --> 00:17:25,920
anything I give him.

280
00:17:27,480 --> 00:17:28,610
He doesn't like you?

281
00:17:31,510 --> 00:17:32,970
"Like" doesn't even begin

282
00:17:33,510 --> 00:17:35,970
to describe
how Li Rongzhang feels about me.

283
00:17:36,510 --> 00:17:37,370
She can't come.

284
00:17:38,240 --> 00:17:38,880
Qingyi.

285
00:17:40,070 --> 00:17:41,870
Miss Fang wants to come herself.

286
00:17:43,000 --> 00:17:43,720
I don't think

287
00:17:43,720 --> 00:17:44,680
Father would mind.

288
00:17:44,680 --> 00:17:45,200
Let's just...

289
00:17:45,200 --> 00:17:46,160
I mind.

290
00:17:59,270 --> 00:17:59,920
Miss Fang.

291
00:18:01,030 --> 00:18:01,640
It's fine.

292
00:18:02,310 --> 00:18:03,310
You guys go ahead.

293
00:18:15,330 --> 00:18:18,650
[Li Residence]

294
00:18:25,790 --> 00:18:26,510
Qingyi,

295
00:18:27,350 --> 00:18:29,200
it's been so long since you came home.

296
00:18:29,200 --> 00:18:31,460
Do you still remember this parasol tree?

297
00:18:32,110 --> 00:18:33,000
I asked Father.

298
00:18:33,400 --> 00:18:34,030
He said

299
00:18:34,400 --> 00:18:36,400
you planted it when you were little.

300
00:18:48,070 --> 00:18:49,070
That's not a parasol tree.

301
00:18:49,070 --> 00:18:49,930
It's a catalpa.

302
00:18:50,510 --> 00:18:52,970
As in "the catalpa trees
of one's hometown."

303
00:18:56,750 --> 00:18:57,270
Qingyi.

304
00:18:58,680 --> 00:19:00,310
The meal is ready.

305
00:19:00,480 --> 00:19:02,210
Father will be here any minute.

306
00:19:10,240 --> 00:19:11,480
I heard he brought back

307
00:19:11,480 --> 00:19:13,410
quite a few bottles of fine liquor.

308
00:19:13,880 --> 00:19:14,880
The three of us can

309
00:19:15,070 --> 00:19:16,930
have a good drink together later.

310
00:19:20,440 --> 00:19:21,570
I asked Father once.

311
00:19:22,590 --> 00:19:23,400
I asked him

312
00:19:23,960 --> 00:19:25,510
why our traditional
Chinese courtyard house

313
00:19:25,510 --> 00:19:27,310
had a Western dining table in it.

314
00:19:27,790 --> 00:19:29,110
He couldn't be bothered to answer me.

315
00:19:29,110 --> 00:19:29,680
Qingyi,

316
00:19:30,350 --> 00:19:31,240
was he like this

317
00:19:31,350 --> 00:19:32,750
when you were little too?

318
00:19:37,270 --> 00:19:39,330
He's always been this insufferable.

319
00:19:41,480 --> 00:19:44,030
He thought sitting so close to everyone
at the round table

320
00:19:44,030 --> 00:19:47,630
didn't show enough of his authority
as the head of the household.

321
00:19:47,960 --> 00:19:49,310
If you ever get the chance,

322
00:19:49,310 --> 00:19:50,770
you can try sitting there.

323
00:19:52,550 --> 00:19:54,880
Sitting in that seat and getting lectured

324
00:19:55,720 --> 00:19:57,110
feels quite different.

325
00:20:04,480 --> 00:20:05,210
You're here.

326
00:20:08,400 --> 00:20:08,880
Father.

327
00:20:18,140 --> 00:20:20,690
[Li Rongzhang, Head of the Li Family,
Marshal of the Ying Army]

328
00:20:21,310 --> 00:20:23,570
Does the Murong family not feed you meat?

329
00:20:23,790 --> 00:20:25,390
Look how thin you've gotten.

330
00:20:29,030 --> 00:20:29,490
Qingyi.

331
00:20:29,960 --> 00:20:30,420
Come on.

332
00:20:31,030 --> 00:20:31,560
Sit here.

333
00:20:46,000 --> 00:20:48,400
At least you still know
where your place is.

334
00:21:19,830 --> 00:21:21,230
You're an inspector now?

335
00:21:24,310 --> 00:21:25,710
How did you know, Father?

336
00:21:26,000 --> 00:21:27,800
Uncle Lin told me over the phone.

337
00:21:29,310 --> 00:21:31,480
He said you're now the youngest inspector.

338
00:21:31,480 --> 00:21:32,680
Keep up the good work.

339
00:21:33,400 --> 00:21:34,330
And don't forget

340
00:21:34,400 --> 00:21:36,130
to repay whoever promoted you.

341
00:21:36,880 --> 00:21:38,080
Don't worry, Father.

342
00:21:38,110 --> 00:21:39,070
I'll do my best.

343
00:21:40,880 --> 00:21:42,080
Since taking office,

344
00:21:42,200 --> 00:21:45,860
the case clearance rate in my district
has gone up significantly.

345
00:21:45,960 --> 00:21:46,440
Father,

346
00:21:46,830 --> 00:21:47,640
you and Qingyi

347
00:21:47,960 --> 00:21:49,820
haven't seen each other in years.

348
00:21:50,070 --> 00:21:51,920
You must have missed him terribly.

349
00:21:51,920 --> 00:21:53,850
I thought that today the three of us

350
00:21:54,030 --> 00:21:56,030
could finally sit down and catch up.

351
00:22:01,350 --> 00:22:02,270
Remember,

352
00:22:03,400 --> 00:22:05,400
you and I are the real father and son.

353
00:22:06,880 --> 00:22:08,590
He's a Murong brat.

354
00:22:10,680 --> 00:22:12,200
I called you here today

355
00:22:13,200 --> 00:22:14,550
to ask when you're

356
00:22:14,550 --> 00:22:16,270
going to marry that Huo girl.

357
00:22:19,030 --> 00:22:20,270
What's it to you?

358
00:22:20,270 --> 00:22:22,400
My army's short on supplies right now.

359
00:22:22,590 --> 00:22:24,440
Let the Huo family provide some arms

360
00:22:24,440 --> 00:22:25,550
as her dowry.

361
00:22:27,790 --> 00:22:29,550
It's just some arms.

362
00:22:30,270 --> 00:22:31,160
Marshal Li,

363
00:22:31,750 --> 00:22:33,550
can't you afford them yourself?

364
00:22:34,270 --> 00:22:35,000
Besides,

365
00:22:35,350 --> 00:22:36,200
isn't it only

366
00:22:36,200 --> 00:22:37,550
the Murong family...

367
00:22:40,240 --> 00:22:42,510
that has the right
to sell me off for arms?

368
00:22:44,600 --> 00:22:46,730
With the Murong family in your corner,

369
00:22:46,920 --> 00:22:48,850
you think you can stand up to me now?

370
00:22:52,510 --> 00:22:53,000
Father,

371
00:22:53,440 --> 00:22:54,370
let's eat first.

372
00:23:01,880 --> 00:23:03,510
Qingyi doesn't have any cutlery.

373
00:23:03,510 --> 00:23:04,910
He doesn't need cutlery.

374
00:23:22,640 --> 00:23:23,550
Eat it.

375
00:23:48,270 --> 00:23:50,070
Did your kitchen make a mistake?

376
00:23:50,160 --> 00:23:51,400
He likes that.

377
00:23:53,750 --> 00:23:55,150
Didn't the Murong family

378
00:23:55,400 --> 00:23:58,110
send you away to study among foreigners?

379
00:24:00,750 --> 00:24:01,960
You should like that.

380
00:24:04,030 --> 00:24:04,590
Eat.

381
00:24:24,070 --> 00:24:27,070
Looks like you've forgotten everything
I taught you.

382
00:24:27,680 --> 00:24:28,350
It's okay.

383
00:24:29,240 --> 00:24:30,440
I'll teach you again.

384
00:24:32,270 --> 00:24:32,750
Eat.

385
00:24:32,880 --> 00:24:33,200
Father.

386
00:24:33,200 --> 00:24:34,130
Stay out of this.

387
00:24:36,240 --> 00:24:37,000
Eat.

388
00:25:37,270 --> 00:25:38,030
Miss Fang.

389
00:25:41,830 --> 00:25:44,160
Marshal, Qingyi forgot the gifts for you,

390
00:25:44,680 --> 00:25:46,410
so I brought them on his behalf.

391
00:25:49,310 --> 00:25:50,000
Qingyi,

392
00:25:50,550 --> 00:25:52,550
they say guests should follow
the host's arrangements,

393
00:25:52,550 --> 00:25:55,160
but a guest should also be considerate
to the host.

394
00:25:55,160 --> 00:25:58,020
If the Li family can't even afford
a kerosene stove,

395
00:25:58,270 --> 00:25:59,800
we could just send one over.

396
00:26:00,240 --> 00:26:01,070
Who is she?

397
00:26:03,720 --> 00:26:04,440
This is

398
00:26:04,550 --> 00:26:05,240
Miss Fang,

399
00:26:05,640 --> 00:26:06,720
Qingyu's fiancée.

400
00:26:08,880 --> 00:26:09,750
From Nanyang.

401
00:26:11,350 --> 00:26:13,880
I've long heard of
your esteemed reputation from Qingyu.

402
00:26:13,880 --> 00:26:15,080
Now that I've met you,

403
00:26:15,680 --> 00:26:16,940
you truly live up to it.

404
00:26:17,440 --> 00:26:19,040
You act like quite the father

405
00:26:19,640 --> 00:26:22,040
when you're lecturing someone else's son.

406
00:26:22,270 --> 00:26:22,960
Miss Fang,

407
00:26:23,880 --> 00:26:26,350
the Li and Murong families
have been close for generations.

408
00:26:26,350 --> 00:26:27,640
Qingyi and I

409
00:26:28,160 --> 00:26:29,590
were switched and raised
by each other's families.

410
00:26:29,590 --> 00:26:30,640
We only returned

411
00:26:30,830 --> 00:26:32,590
to our birth families at the age of 12.

412
00:26:32,590 --> 00:26:33,880
So Qingyi and Father

413
00:26:34,200 --> 00:26:35,800
are like real father and son.

414
00:26:36,240 --> 00:26:37,110
That's just bullshit

415
00:26:37,110 --> 00:26:38,240
to fool those

416
00:26:38,240 --> 00:26:40,030
gossiping busybodies outside.

417
00:26:40,030 --> 00:26:40,680
Father.

418
00:26:40,790 --> 00:26:42,920
The Murongs have always cared
too much about their reputation.

419
00:26:42,920 --> 00:26:43,790
I don't.

420
00:26:44,350 --> 00:26:46,410
So what if there was a mix-up at birth?

421
00:26:46,510 --> 00:26:48,200
What's there to hide?

422
00:26:49,590 --> 00:26:50,520
I'm telling you,

423
00:26:51,070 --> 00:26:51,510
I

424
00:26:51,790 --> 00:26:53,030
raised him.

425
00:26:53,400 --> 00:26:56,000
Do you think
I have the right to discipline him?

426
00:27:04,030 --> 00:27:06,160
Then I was the one who spoke out of turn.

427
00:27:22,720 --> 00:27:24,780
Allow me to drink this cup as a penalty

428
00:27:24,790 --> 00:27:27,000
and a toast to you for raising Qingyi.

429
00:27:34,830 --> 00:27:36,240
Since when does

430
00:27:36,240 --> 00:27:38,030
an outsider like you, a mere junior,

431
00:27:38,030 --> 00:27:39,630
have the right to speak to me?

432
00:27:40,480 --> 00:27:42,750
Before you, I'm merely a junior, Marshal.

433
00:27:42,750 --> 00:27:44,550
But as Qingyi's future sister-in-law,

434
00:27:44,550 --> 00:27:46,680
it's only right that I look out for him.

435
00:27:48,920 --> 00:27:49,850
Look out for him?

436
00:27:50,790 --> 00:27:52,160
Oh, that's rich.

437
00:27:57,240 --> 00:27:58,640
Come with me to the study.

438
00:27:58,720 --> 00:28:00,250
I have something to ask you.

439
00:28:06,790 --> 00:28:07,960
You're a Murong.

440
00:28:08,680 --> 00:28:10,750
You don't have to take orders from him.

441
00:28:10,750 --> 00:28:12,080
This is my own business.

442
00:28:13,720 --> 00:28:15,320
It has nothing to do with you.

443
00:28:30,920 --> 00:28:31,720
Inspector Li,

444
00:28:33,160 --> 00:28:34,360
your family really is

445
00:28:35,240 --> 00:28:37,040
the picture of filial devotion.

446
00:28:37,310 --> 00:28:38,440
I didn't expect it

447
00:28:39,240 --> 00:28:40,500
to be like this either.

448
00:29:02,750 --> 00:29:03,720
Get in here.

449
00:29:28,830 --> 00:29:29,430
Come here.

450
00:29:30,400 --> 00:29:31,640
Light my pipe.

451
00:29:37,480 --> 00:29:39,280
What are you putting on airs for?

452
00:29:40,110 --> 00:29:42,550
You really think a few years
with the Murong family

453
00:29:42,550 --> 00:29:44,810
turned you into some refined gentleman?

454
00:29:44,920 --> 00:29:45,880
Listen up.

455
00:29:46,480 --> 00:29:47,790
To me,

456
00:29:48,480 --> 00:29:51,750
you'll always be the jinx
who got your mother killed.

457
00:29:55,030 --> 00:29:57,400
My father has spent years away
on military campaigns

458
00:29:57,400 --> 00:29:58,800
and has rarely been home.

459
00:29:58,920 --> 00:30:01,350
After Qingyi returned to
the Murong family,

460
00:30:01,350 --> 00:30:02,480
he studied overseas

461
00:30:02,960 --> 00:30:04,620
and later worked in Beicheng.

462
00:30:05,590 --> 00:30:06,720
For the past 3 years,

463
00:30:07,270 --> 00:30:09,530
they haven't even seen each other at all.

464
00:30:13,680 --> 00:30:15,240
My father may be a rough man,

465
00:30:17,030 --> 00:30:18,270
but I've always felt

466
00:30:18,790 --> 00:30:20,160
the deep love and care

467
00:30:20,440 --> 00:30:21,400
he has for me.

468
00:30:21,720 --> 00:30:23,350
So I never imagined

469
00:30:24,030 --> 00:30:26,160
that things between him and Qingyi...

470
00:30:27,110 --> 00:30:27,970
I didn't expect

471
00:30:28,680 --> 00:30:29,960
their relationship

472
00:30:30,720 --> 00:30:31,880
to be this bad.

473
00:30:37,480 --> 00:30:38,070
Then...

474
00:30:40,680 --> 00:30:43,010
what about your mother from the Li family?

475
00:30:56,920 --> 00:30:58,450
What happened to your hand?

476
00:31:02,070 --> 00:31:03,730
Compared to what you did to me,

477
00:31:04,640 --> 00:31:05,510
it's nothing.

478
00:31:10,000 --> 00:31:11,440
Now you're with the Murong family,

479
00:31:11,440 --> 00:31:13,790
and you can't even
keep yourself in one piece?

480
00:31:13,790 --> 00:31:15,000
How did I raise you?

481
00:31:17,110 --> 00:31:17,880
Useless.

482
00:31:23,200 --> 00:31:24,310
If that's all,

483
00:31:25,030 --> 00:31:25,960
I'll be leaving.

484
00:31:26,640 --> 00:31:27,640
Stop right there.

485
00:31:29,960 --> 00:31:32,240
You got a batch of planes
for Murong Qingyu.

486
00:31:32,240 --> 00:31:33,480
Yet when I ask you for some arms,

487
00:31:33,480 --> 00:31:34,920
you keep dragging your feet.

488
00:31:34,920 --> 00:31:36,790
Just marry that Huo woman already.

489
00:31:36,790 --> 00:31:38,750
I don't have that much time
to waste on you.

490
00:31:38,750 --> 00:31:40,550
Who told you I'm going to marry her?

491
00:31:40,550 --> 00:31:42,210
Who else would you marry then?

492
00:31:42,550 --> 00:31:43,920
That Nyonya?

493
00:31:49,790 --> 00:31:51,320
Useless, just as I thought—

494
00:31:52,030 --> 00:31:55,160
too much of a coward to marry
the woman you actually want.

495
00:31:59,030 --> 00:32:01,760
Your brother gets to
walk off with the prize, huh?

496
00:32:05,920 --> 00:32:07,000
If you don't dare to marry her,

497
00:32:07,000 --> 00:32:08,600
I'll snatch her away myself.

498
00:32:10,110 --> 00:32:11,040
What did you say?

499
00:32:11,640 --> 00:32:12,440
I said,

500
00:32:13,110 --> 00:32:15,570
I'll snatch her
and make her your new mother.

501
00:32:16,640 --> 00:32:18,030
You dare defy me now, huh?

502
00:32:18,030 --> 00:32:19,160
Look at your mother!

503
00:32:19,440 --> 00:32:21,110
Am I wrong to call you useless?

504
00:32:22,070 --> 00:32:23,600
Look at your mother's face!

505
00:32:23,790 --> 00:32:26,250
And you still dare deny
that I'm your father?

506
00:32:26,640 --> 00:32:28,920
Mother, I'm hungry.

507
00:32:30,030 --> 00:32:30,750
I'm hungry!

508
00:32:32,920 --> 00:32:33,400
Mother.

509
00:32:33,400 --> 00:32:34,480
Hungry? You're hungry?

510
00:32:34,480 --> 00:32:35,680
You dare to be hungry?

511
00:32:36,270 --> 00:32:37,680
If you hadn't been
such a disobedient child,

512
00:32:37,680 --> 00:32:39,510
would your father
have treated us this way?

513
00:32:39,510 --> 00:32:40,790
If he threw us out,

514
00:32:40,790 --> 00:32:42,030
where would we sleep?

515
00:32:42,270 --> 00:32:44,240
We'd end up on the streets,
and no one would care about us!

516
00:32:44,240 --> 00:32:45,350
Do you understand?

517
00:32:45,750 --> 00:32:47,610
All you ever say is you're hungry.

518
00:32:50,750 --> 00:32:51,310
I...

519
00:32:53,200 --> 00:32:54,530
I didn't have an affair.

520
00:32:56,270 --> 00:32:57,510
I didn't have an affair.

521
00:32:57,510 --> 00:32:59,510
We have to be good.

522
00:33:00,480 --> 00:33:01,960
That way, your father will love us.

523
00:33:01,960 --> 00:33:03,200
He'll be good to us.

524
00:33:03,200 --> 00:33:04,790
He won't kick us out.

525
00:33:04,790 --> 00:33:06,240
Do you understand?

526
00:33:07,110 --> 00:33:08,790
Don't listen to the servants' nonsense.

527
00:33:08,790 --> 00:33:10,680
You are the child of your father and me.

528
00:33:10,680 --> 00:33:11,740
Don't cry anymore.

529
00:33:12,160 --> 00:33:12,960
Be good.

530
00:33:13,240 --> 00:33:15,240
Then your father will treat us well.

531
00:33:15,240 --> 00:33:16,400
We won't be kicked out,

532
00:33:16,400 --> 00:33:18,660
and we won't have to sleep on the streets!

533
00:33:23,750 --> 00:33:25,750
My birth mother passed away very early.

534
00:33:25,750 --> 00:33:27,350
I never got the chance to meet her.

535
00:33:27,350 --> 00:33:29,240
Qingyi spent more time with her.

536
00:33:29,790 --> 00:33:30,400
I think...

537
00:33:32,400 --> 00:33:33,730
my birth mother's death

538
00:33:34,400 --> 00:33:36,480
must have left a deep scar on him.

539
00:33:39,440 --> 00:33:41,170
If it weren't for you back then,

540
00:33:41,790 --> 00:33:44,050
your mother wouldn't have died so young!

541
00:33:45,590 --> 00:33:46,440
I've always

542
00:33:47,000 --> 00:33:49,130
treasured the bond Qingyi and I share.

543
00:33:50,160 --> 00:33:52,360
But he's always been so distant with me.

544
00:33:52,880 --> 00:33:54,740
I foolishly believed that was...

545
00:33:55,590 --> 00:33:57,120
that was simply his nature.

546
00:34:00,160 --> 00:34:01,270
Now I realize...

547
00:34:05,240 --> 00:34:06,040
Inspector Li,

548
00:34:08,360 --> 00:34:10,219
you're one of the fortunate ones.

549
00:34:10,630 --> 00:34:13,030
You don't know the pain
of the unfortunate.

550
00:34:14,880 --> 00:34:16,630
You dare raise your hand against me?

551
00:34:16,630 --> 00:34:18,030
Getting some nerve, huh?

552
00:34:25,320 --> 00:34:25,780
Father!

553
00:34:25,960 --> 00:34:26,420
Father!

554
00:34:26,550 --> 00:34:27,150
Father...

555
00:34:27,440 --> 00:34:27,900
Father.

556
00:34:29,670 --> 00:34:30,190
Father.

557
00:34:33,590 --> 00:34:35,449
Nice job beating him up, Marshal.

558
00:34:35,920 --> 00:34:37,440
Tomorrow's headlines
across all the Nancheng tabloids

559
00:34:37,440 --> 00:34:38,770
will write themselves.

560
00:34:39,760 --> 00:34:41,620
A father teaching his son a lesson

561
00:34:41,840 --> 00:34:42,920
is only natural.

562
00:34:46,150 --> 00:34:48,080
If Qingyi has done anything wrong,

563
00:34:48,110 --> 00:34:49,510
we will discipline him.

564
00:34:50,510 --> 00:34:52,150
You have no right to step in.

565
00:34:55,510 --> 00:34:58,110
Even if Murong Feng himself
were standing here today,

566
00:34:58,110 --> 00:34:59,510
he wouldn't dare stop me.

567
00:35:03,000 --> 00:35:04,510
Who do you think you are?

568
00:35:10,760 --> 00:35:12,400
Just like your dead mother—

569
00:35:12,590 --> 00:35:14,450
you don't even know your own kind.

570
00:35:15,670 --> 00:35:16,230
Useless.

571
